<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.georgerrmartin.com" class="external text" title="http://www.georgerrmartin.com" rel="nofollow">GeorgeRRMartin.com</a> - George R. R. Martin's website</li>
<li><a href="http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/" class="external text" title="http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/" rel="nofollow">The Citadel</a> at <a href="http://www.westeros.org" class="external text" title="http://www.westeros.org" rel="nofollow">www.westeros.org</a> - extensive archive about the series, including detailed thematic notes, timelines, artwork &amp; <a href="/wiki/Heraldry" title="Heraldry">heraldry</a>, and correspondence from the author</li>
<li><a href="http://asoiaf.westeros.org" class="external text" title="http://asoiaf.westeros.org" rel="nofollow">Westeros Forum</a> - a popular and busy forum based around discussion of the series and its spin-offs</li>
<li><a href="http://www.towerofthehand.com" class="external text" title="http://www.towerofthehand.com" rel="nofollow">Tower of the Hand: An Encyclopaedia of Ice and Fire</a> - A comprehensive treatment of A Song of Ice and Fire with chapter summaries and individual pages for every character, location, historical event, noble house, etc. from the series all thoroughly cross-referenced and hyperlinked</li>
<li><a href="http://en.amokanet.ru/gallery/martin/" class="external text" title="http://en.amokanet.ru/gallery/martin/" rel="nofollow">Amoka.net Gallery</a> Fan-created <a href="/wiki/Portrait" title="Portrait">portraits</a> and scenes of the Song of Ice and Fire characters</li>
<li><a href="http://www.bwbfanclub.com" class="external text" title="http://www.bwbfanclub.com" rel="nofollow">BwB Fan Club</a> - GRRM fan club</li>
