<li><a href="http://www.isfdb.org/cgi-bin/pe.cgi?A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire" class="external text" title="http://www.isfdb.org/cgi-bin/pe.cgi?A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire" rel="nofollow">A Song of Ice and Fire</a> series listing at the <a href="/wiki/Internet_Speculative_Fiction_Database" title="Internet Speculative Fiction Database" class="mw-redirect">Internet Speculative Fiction Database</a></li>
